{
  "info": {
    "name": "PolicyEval - All API",
    "_postman_id": "policyeval-all-collection",
    "description": "Complete API Collection untuk Platform Evaluasi Kebijakan Lingkungan Sekolah.\n\n## Base URL\nSemua request menggunakan base URL: `{{baseUrl}}/api/v1`\n\n## Response Format\n\n**Success (List):**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": true,\n  \"message\": \"...\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"contents\": [],\n    \"meta\": { \"page\": 1, \"limit\": 10, \"total\": 100 }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Success (Single):**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": true,\n  \"message\": \"...\",\n  \"data\": {}\n}\n```\n\n**Error:**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": false,\n  \"message\": \"...\",\n  \"errors\": []\n}\n```",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "authToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Authentication endpoints (Login, Logout, Profile)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin@cbt.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Login Success (Admin)",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Login successful\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"token\": \"1|abc123...\",\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"name\": \"Administrator\",\n      \"email\": \"admin@cbt.com\",\n      \"role\": \"ADMIN\"\n    }\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Login Failed - Wrong Password",
              "code": 401,
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Username atau password salah\",\n  \"errors\": []\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Login Failed - Validation",
              "code": 422,
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Validation failed\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"username\": [\"The username field is required.\"],\n    \"password\": [\"The password field is required.\"]\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "logout"]
            }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Logout Success",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Logged out successfully\",\n  \"data\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/profile",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "profile"]
            }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Profile Success",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Administrator\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@cbt.com\",\n    \"role\": \"ADMIN\"\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
